# Optional per-process Pythia8 shower overrides. Rename to `pythia8.cmnd` to use
# INSTEAD of cards/defaults/pythia8.cmnd. Only needed if this process wants
# different shower/hadronization settings. Beams:LHEF, HEPMCoutput:file, and
# Main:numberOfEvents are injected by stage 02 — keep this to physics knobs.
